OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe Big Plastic Count:     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSurvey shows 'recycling    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdoesn't work'              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The organisers of Britain's biggest    
OL,6, ever survey of household plastic waste 
OL,7, have called for immediate action to    
OL,8, tackle what they say are "jaw-dropping"
OL,9, findings.                              
OL,11,FThe Big Plastic Count was run across a 
OL,12,Fweek in May and its results show that  
OL,13,Fthe average participating household    
OL,14,Fthrew away 66 pieces of plastic in a   
OL,15,Fweek.                                  
OL,17,FUsing those figures the organisers,    
OL,18,FGreenpeace and Everyday Plastic,       
OL,19,Festimate that the UK throws out nearly 
OL,20,F100 billion pieces of plastic a year.  
